<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>List of exceptions</title>
    {% include 'head.jinja2' %}

</head>
<body>

<style type='text/css'>
	.exception {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: red;
		white-space: pre-wrap;
		margin-bottom: 3em;
	}
</style>

{% if exceptions | length == 0 %}
	<p>No exceptions were generated. </p>
{% else %}
	<p>These are the exceptions obtained so far (most recent first):</p>
{% endif %}

{% for e in exceptions | reverse %}
<pre class='exception'>{{e}}</pre>
{% endfor %}

{% if url_refresh is defined %}
<p> If the problem is that something is not found
because of stale caches, <a href='{{url_refresh}}'>try to refresh the library</a>.
{% endif %}

</body>
</html>
